Drivers who do not manage the required exchange by the end of the year and leave without a valid driver's license, will face a fine from January.
The perpetrator pays a maximum of 2,000 crowns.
However, the police can also have it reversed with an admonition.
In the event of a violation, the penalty may be increased to 2500 kroner.
According to previous information, the municipality may also impose a penalty on those who do not drive at all.
